DATASETS:

=====

NAME: rotten-imdb (modality task, sentence based):

URL: http://www.cs.cornell.edu/people/pabo/movie-review-data/rotten_imdb.tar.gz

=====

NAME: polarity-dataset (sentiment task):

- TYPE: v1 (sentence based):
    URL: https://www.cs.cornell.edu/people/pabo/movie-review-data/rt-polaritydata.tar.gz

- TYPE: v2 (text based):
    URL: https://www.cs.cornell.edu/people/pabo/movie-review-data/review_polarity.tar.gz

=====

NAME: acl-imdb (sentiment task, text based):

URL: https://ai.stanford.edu/~amaas/data/sentiment/aclImdb_v1.tar.gz

